== What is it? ==

The Universal Rail Type is a [[en/Manual/NewGRF]] for OpenTTD which makes the replacement of trains easier when converting between rail types e.g. conversion between normal rail and monorail. 

== Where can I get it? ==

The easiest way is to obtain it using the online content service. Search for "Universal Rail Type" ingame to automatically install, or visit [http://bananas.openttd.org/en/newgrf BaNaNaS], search for "Universal Rail Type" and click the download counter for a manual install.

